content:
To add a logo next to the header, you can include an image element within the header element, like this: ```html

Denti.AI Hygenius

shared dialog

``` In this example, I added an `img` element before the `h1` element inside the `header` element. I set the `src` attribute to the URL or path of your logo image, and the `alt` attribute to a brief description of your logo. You can then style the logo using CSS, for example by setting its `width` or `height` properties, or by positioning it using `float` or `display: inline-block`.
